{"type": "article", "id": 12559, "title": "Adidas “Artwork”系列作品", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-24T08:09:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000208pidVf8rX3BcmvtFl.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近来，Adidas 与 Pharrell Williams 携手推出 Supershell 企划，他们邀请了纽约艺术家 Todd James，著名建筑师 Zaha Hadid，日本艺术家 Mr. （<span>他是</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">村上隆的得意门生</span>）以及摄影师 Cass Bird 这四位艺术家，改造 Adidas 经典的贝壳头，同时，Pharrell 自身也有作品加入，用户可以自由选择搭配。Pharrell Williams x Supershell x adidas Originals 的这个系列将限量发售，<a href=\"http://www.adidas.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以关注。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261403135Zs8VONIgfqYRcd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42176039\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261403141am7BVcHD8oSl24v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140314fbOk1iT2gIZYXLs0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140314nFHyrEaG46buJe15.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140316eDFxpWcbCnQyz9qM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.28484108\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}